parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine to stall or hesitate, leading to loss of power and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The check engine light stays on
the vehicle accelerates slowly
the engine stalls without warning
the vehicle hesitates or loses power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to find a dealership to perform recall repairs can lead to prolonged exposure to safety risks and financial burdens on the vehicle owner.
symptoms: Difficulty finding a dealership to perform recall repairs
dealerships refusing to perform recall repairs
dealerships claiming that parts are not included in the recall
dealerships being out of operation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden stalling of the engine can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning
the vehicle hesitates or loses power
the vehicle stalls while driving at high speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hose can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distance, and potentially, accidents.
symptoms: The ABS light illuminates on the dashboard
the front wheels lock when applying the brakes
the vehicle has a history of frequent brake replacements.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the brakes to malfunction, leading to reduced stopping power, increased stopping distance, and potentially, accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle has a history of frequent brake replacements
the brakes are prone to premature wear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to obtain recall repairs can lead to continued operation of a vehicle with a known safety defect, potentially causing accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The dealer is no longer in operation
the consumer is unable to find a dealer to perform the recall repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag control module can cause the airbag light to illuminate, indicating a potential malfunction of the airbag system, which can lead to unintended airbag deployment or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, resulting in serious injury or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light illuminates on the dashboard
the airbag deploys unexpectedly
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
chemical burns or injuries from airbag deployment.
